{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-21-2",
 "title": "The Interrogation of Moff Tazecks",
 "summary": "In the detention block of the NRSC Deliverance, Captain Howie Darklighter assembles Luke Skywalker, NRI interrogator Jonau Diggs, and several guards to question the captured, sedated Sith Moff Morganna Tazecks about the new Death Star. Luke uses the Force to rouse and restrain her mind while Diggs and Darklighter press her with measured, almost gentle questions, promising her eventual return to Selene in exchange for cooperation. As Diggs probes verbally, Luke covertly tears through Morganna's memories, confirming she knows little beyond the weapon's existence but uncovering hints about Lord Valak, a Krayt Dragon bought from Jack Raven, and a jungle. Enraged at the violation, Morganna lunges and bites Luke's shoulder before the guards stun her into unconsciousness. The frustrated team withdraws with scant new intelligence, and Darklighter departs to arrange transport to Caspar.",
